{"tid":1868641,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［健康常識］腰痛係病假既常見原因，壓力大可能會引致腰痛","createTime":"2020-02-07T16:34:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-08T14:57:55.000Z","uid":40478,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0e0d0866fb7b5b4ad521e609915b5a9c3fc3f7bc","tid":1868641,"uid":40478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T16:34:24.000Z","msg":"腰病係全世界最常見既一個請病假原因<br />\n而痛症可以係由生理、心理同社交既原因引發<span style=\"color: red;\">壓力大係引發腰痛既重要因素</span><br />\n腰痛唔一定由生理原因做成，同由病毒細菌引起既，有生理成因既傷風感冒唔同。有無流鼻水、肺有無雜聲、喉嚨有無發炎，呢d叫 signs，係睇得到既病徵，係扮唔到既；而腰痛可以係無signs，只有主觀既Symptoms（症狀）， 腰痛患者腰骨未必有退化、發炎，可能照完x光乜事都無，但咁並唔代表佢地既痛症係假既，只係由於痛症係成因係psycho-social，所以難D用儀器探測到咁解姐<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">舉個例子，罷工既醫護憂心國事，又怕比人清算，壓力太大引起腰痛都好正常，搵個醫生寫好醫生信</span>，休息番幾個月，都好合理呀，身體要緊呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaff6be229a596db82afb9b5aaa58729ce1c9fa2","tid":1868641,"uid":40478,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T16:37:03.000Z","msg":"健康post無人理"},{"pid":"62be9180feb27a23cf6ef2d514bfa87b3721785e","tid":1868641,"uid":281775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T16:46:27.000Z","msg":"腰痛可大可少啊<br />\n醫生 nurses 助理 甚至推床的姐姐真係好辛苦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa95c57908a7cd9c8de48e403ebe744d89b541a6","tid":1868641,"uid":40478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T05:01:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a2d9b9cb9f5903ce02b2de4ac0bb91a4bb79b9b","tid":1868641,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T14:50:49.000Z","msg":"使撚腰痛，企得多都腳痛啦"},{"pid":"3bc73aa6c823f8f683ccd1e319d930dfb5fcbb91","tid":1868641,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T14:57:55.000Z","msg":"推"}]}